OL,3,CStudent renter 'totally isolated'
OL,4,Cafter shock eviction notice
OL,6,FA student renter says she was 'totally
OL,7,Fisolated' after being the victim of a
OL,8,F"no-fault" eviction in a house that
OL,9,Fdid not comply with safety regulations.
OL,11,FSarah Crowley, from Whalley Range in
OL,12,FManchester, was left without hot water
OL,13,Fin her previous home for six months
OL,14,Fbecause of an issue with the boiler
OL,15,Fsupply.
OL,17,FShe reached out to her estate agent,
OL,18,Fbut was told they were not contactable
OL,19,Fbecause they were out of the country
OL,20,Fworking as a missionary.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
