OL,3,CStudent renter 'totally isolated'
OL,4,Cafter shock eviction notice
OL,6,FShe then received an unexpected
OL,7,FSection 21 notice around Christmas
OL,8,Ftime in 2017, which allows landlords
OL,9,Fto evict their tenants without a
OL,10,Fspecific reason.
OL,12,FSarah said: "I was in a really dark
OL,13,Fplace. I had a lot of anxiety attacks.
OL,14,FIt just exacerbated all of my health
OL,15,Fconditions.
OL,17,F"It was quite scary to be like 'you
OL,18,Fmight be homeless', or 'you might be
OL,19,Fon the street'."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
