OL,3,CStudent renter 'totally isolated'
OL,4,Cafter shock eviction notice
OL,6,F"I have needs because I had an
OL,7,Faccident when I was really young," she
OL,8,Fadded.
OL,10,F"I can get shakes and anxiety attacks.
OL,11,FThose things did happen at that time."
OL,13,FIt transpired that the landlord was
OL,14,Funable to sell the property as certain
OL,15,Fwork, including the hot water issue,
OL,16,Fneeded to be carried out first to
OL,17,Fallow it to be sold.
OL,19,FFor all of the time she was living
OL,20,Fthere, the property did not comply
OL,21,Fwith the safety regulations.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
