OL,6,FSarah said she fears for families who
OL,7,Fmay be in the same position. "It's
OL,8,Fjust me on my own but I dread to think
OL,9,Fwhat its like with a family, with
OL,10,Fsmall kids.
OL,12,F"Having to live in a hotel room or
OL,13,Fsomething that compact, of that size.
OL,14,FThat's something that happened
OL,15,Fcenturies ago, you don't expect that
OL,16,Fto happen now."
OL,18,FShe said she didn't feel that her
OL,19,Flandlord cared about her, and found it
OL,20,Fvery difficult to contact them.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
