OL,3,CStudent renter 'totally isolated'
OL,4,Cafter shock eviction notice
OL,6,F"I felt like I was hitting a brick
OL,7,Fwall. Totally isolated. I'm just a
OL,8,Fperson paying money for a property.
OL,9,FThere doesn't seem to be that care
OL,10,Fwhich is important.
OL,12,F"We're not just a pound sign, we're
OL,13,Factually people."
OL,15,FSarah Crowley complained about her hot
OL,16,Fwater issues numerous times, and did
OL,17,Fnot feel like the necessary support
OL,18,Fwas provided.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
