OL,6,FSarah spoke to a homeless charity and
OL,7,Fwas advised to declare herself
OL,8,Fhomeless.
OL,10,F"It felt a bit like 'why me, what have
OL,11,FI done wrong?" she said.
OL,13,F"As a tenant, I might be renting but I
OL,14,Fstill have a right to have a decent
OL,15,Fhome. My basic needs should be met
OL,16,Flike hot water, a roof over my head,
OL,17,Fheating. It just seemed to not really
OL,18,Fbe there."
OL,20,FThe Government has said it will bring
OL,21,Fan end to "no-fault" evictions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
