OL,3,CStudent renter 'totally isolated'
OL,4,Cafter shock eviction notice
OL,6,FThe Renters Rights Bill returned to
OL,7,Fthe House of Commons for its third
OL,8,Freading on Tuesday 14 January.
OL,10,FIt is expected to include new
OL,11,Fregulations which the Government says
OL,12,Fwill improve living conditions and
OL,13,Fhelp to protect renters.
OL,15,FThis could involve new deadlines for
OL,16,Flandlords to tackle dangerous
OL,17,Fconditions.
OL,19,FIt is also likely that landlords will
OL,20,Fno longer be able to refuse to rent to
OL,21,Fpeople on benefits.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
