OL,6,FLandlords warn it could have some
OL,7,Funintended effects, such as landlords
OL,8,Flisting at a higher rent to mitigate
OL,9,Fthe risk of renters signing a tenancy
OL,10,Fand immediately serving notice.
OL,12,FThe National Residential Landlords
OL,13,FAssociation (NRLA) say it could lead
OL,14,Fto "AirBNB lite", as tenants could be
OL,15,Fable to give two months' notice as
OL,16,Fsoon as they move in.
OL,18,FBen Beadle from the NRLA said:
OL,19,F"Landlords need to have confidence, if
OL,20,Fthey don't have confidence they won't
OL,21,Finvest, they won't stay in the market.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
