OL,6,F"Despite promises around additional
OL,7,Fnew homes being built, 1.5 million in
OL,8,Fthis Parliament, I'm going to be a
OL,9,Fvery old man by the time we we see
OL,10,Fthat come to fruition.
OL,12,F"The housing crisis is now, and we
OL,13,Fneed to have balance between giving
OL,14,Frenters greater rights, but also
OL,15,Fmaking sure that landlords can still
OL,16,Foperate, because the government needs
OL,17,Flandlords."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
