OL,6,FAngela Rayner, Secretary of State for
OL,7,FHousing said: "I'm calling time on
OL,8,Fthose that are not giving renters the
OL,9,Fprotections they deserve."
OL,11,F"Nobody should be living in a home
OL,12,Fthat is not safe."
